{
  "id": "69f53f760e5def139848ae9a",
  "title": "2026/05/06",
  "created": 1777680248,
  "updated": 1778136275,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f53f760e5def139848ae9a",
      "text": "2026/05/06",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777680248,
      "updated": 1777680248
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa1fac6eb4060000009cf510",
      "text": "第19週: 日月火[[水]]木金土",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777999788,
      "updated": 1777999788
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa1fac6eb406000000e23655",
      "text": "2026年 34.52％経過",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777999788,
      "updated": 1777999788
    },
    {
      "id": "69f53f770000000000e56edd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1777680248,
      "updated": 1778029044
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa24b10000000000c75fc1",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778001074,
      "updated": 1778001076
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa24b40000000000c75fc2",
      "text": "　[プロパガンダム]、なにこれw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778001076,
      "updated": 1778001094
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa9c6d0000000000c75fca",
      "text": "　　プロパガンダをリンクにしようとしたときにこれが出てきてフフっとなった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778031726,
      "updated": 1778031747
    },
    {
      "id": "69fadd200000000000ff5203",
      "text": "　　[風呂がパンダ]も同時期に生み出されていた[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1778048288,
      "updated": 1778048308
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0a3e000000000084bab1",
      "text": "　　[プロパーカンダタ][who.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778059839,
      "updated": 1778059843
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa24c60000000000c75fc3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778001094,
      "updated": 1778001095
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa53f40000000000b972e3",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013172,
      "updated": 1778013172
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa53f50000000000b972e4",
      "text": "\t今日も休日か。日記などから多角的に調べた",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013173,
      "updated": 1778026390
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa54270000000000b972e5",
      "text": "\t\t明らかに明日から出社という前提で色々組まれているので、この過去の自分を信じるべきだろう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013224,
      "updated": 1778013241
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa543b0000000000b972e6",
      "text": "\t\tそもそもマイクラバーサスが今日なのもGW最終日狙ってのことでしょう",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013243,
      "updated": 1778013440
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa53f40000000000b972e2",
      "text": "\tアスリート気質の俺は休日も、一仕事終えた休暇残りも、維持のための時間を取ろうとするが、これでは休憩にならない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013172,
      "updated": 1778013293
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa546d0000000000b972e8",
      "text": "\t\tというわけで[戦国無双4]買って遊んでる、昨日買って昨日だけで10時間遊んだｗ",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013293,
      "updated": 1778013314
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafbfa0000000000cc14da",
      "text": "\t\t\t17:29:50 ここまでで16時間。18:00からマイクラバーサス見て寝るので今日はおしまい、もうメシも歯磨きも皿洗いも全部済ませて、このあと風呂沸いたら入ってからバーサス",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778056188,
      "updated": 1778056226
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafc210000000000cc14db",
      "text": "\t\t\t万全すぎる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778056226,
      "updated": 1778056236
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa557e0000000000b972ef",
      "text": "\t\tこういう判断も生成AIのおかげかもしれない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013566,
      "updated": 1778013585
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa548d0000000000b972ea",
      "text": "\t\t\t[Cosenseで生成AIも使った週次レビューをする]してて、AIが「いや休んだ方がいいよ」提案してきた",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013325,
      "updated": 1778013411
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa55140000000000b972eb",
      "text": "\t\t\tひとりでは気づきにくいし、気付いても「うるせえ俺は知的生産者《アスリート》なんだよ」「[/stao/ぼく人間ちゃうわ。知的生産者や]」などとしがち",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013460,
      "updated": 1778013535
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa72e30000000000aac998",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778021092,
      "updated": 1778021092
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa72e30000000000aac999",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778021092,
      "updated": 1778021095
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa72e70000000000aac99a",
      "text": " ほう。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778021097,
      "updated": 1778021103
    },
    {
      "id": "69fac82f00000000008c4ef1",
      "text": " [ヒトナー]第4話読んだ。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778042932,
      "updated": 1778086589
    },
    {
      "id": "69fac83700000000008c4ef2",
      "text": " \t読み切り時で完成していたと思っていたが広がるもんだな。すごい。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778042935,
      "updated": 1778042946
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad85200000000001c6145",
      "text": " 4月と5月のカレンダーを並べて貼っていたのだけど、うっかり4月を貼りっぱなしにしていた。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778047059,
      "updated": 1778047081
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad86800000000001c6146",
      "text": " \tさっき、パタリと4月のカレンダーだけが落ちた。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778047081,
      "updated": 1778047094
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad87900000000001c6147",
      "text": " \t終わりを自ら告げるタイプの子だった。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778047097,
      "updated": 1778047125
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad99300000000002febaa",
      "text": " コーヒーカップに、日本酒の如く縁までなみなみとコーヒーをうっかり注がれる。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778047380,
      "updated": 1778047408
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad9b200000000002febab",
      "text": " \t慎重にすすった。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778047410,
      "updated": 1778047445
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb082e00000000005f45f4",
      "text": " へえ、こんなものが。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778059311,
      "updated": 1778059314
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb083200000000005f45f5",
      "text": " \t✂ to [人文ウォッチに同人誌インデックス機能]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778059315,
      "updated": 1778059453
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa55710000000000b972ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778013554,
      "updated": 1778013554
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7ae800000000006a6a10",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023145,
      "updated": 1778023151
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7aef00000000006a6a12",
      "text": "\tおはようございます。今日も一日、ご安寧に。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023152,
      "updated": 1778023167
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7f3700000000006a6a22",
      "text": "\tアウトライン形式の文の先頭にフィラーをつけると、文のレベルを揃えることができる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778024248,
      "updated": 1778024304
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7c2700000000006a6a14",
      "text": "\tえーと（フィラー）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023464,
      "updated": 1778024234
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7fd600000000006a6a24",
      "text": " \t✂ [常在有事の変な人]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778024407,
      "updated": 1778024628
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa80bb00000000006a6a25",
      "text": " \t切り出せるくらいの内容はタイトルが思いつかない場合は先頭にフィラーを置いておくとキレイに見える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778024636,
      "updated": 1778024674
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa9dfc0000000000e347fd",
      "text": " Last Visited でソートした時に国旗が上の方に上がってくるのなんでなんだろう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778032126,
      "updated": 1778032144
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa9e0f0000000000e347fe",
      "text": " \tなんで勝手そりゃあ当然、誰かが見てるからなんだけど。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778032144,
      "updated": 1778032162
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa9e2c0000000000e347ff",
      "text": " \tおもろい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778032173,
      "updated": 1778032175
    },
    {
      "id": "69faab9100000000003108e5",
      "text": " 井戸の底を見に行ったらこんな物が。懐かしい。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778035602,
      "updated": 1778035615
    },
    {
      "id": "69faab9e00000000003108e6",
      "text": "  → [不具合を修正不可能と判断しサービス終了]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778035615,
      "updated": 1778112374
    },
    {
      "id": "69faac1800000000003108e7",
      "text": "  技術的困難の中でも最悪の事態だろうなぁ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778035737,
      "updated": 1778035788
    },
    {
      "id": "69fabbcb000000000031090a",
      "text": " ✂ [心神耗弱状態での言動に対するド詰めは止めてあげて欲しい]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778039756,
      "updated": 1778112364
    },
    {
      "id": "69fae75700000000001294de",
      "text": " ✂ [人を守るべき弱者として扱う話し方はして良いものなのかどうか悩む]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778050905,
      "updated": 1778112161
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb582a0000000000656b9a",
      "text": " 謎に激しい頭痛に見舞われてビックリしている",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778079787,
      "updated": 1778079787
    },
    {
      "id": "69fae77300000000001294df",
      "text": "  熱が37度ある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778050932,
      "updated": 1778051210
    },
    {
      "id": "69fae89600000000001294e0",
      "text": "  華氏100度ジョークをするには足りない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778051223,
      "updated": 1778051257
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafc3d00000000004406e5",
      "text": "  お大事に[onuma.icon][caki.icon][vlzs.icon][seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "5eb247ae6474d4001ea56fda",
      "created": 1778056253,
      "updated": 1778058401
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7ae800000000006a6a11",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023145,
      "updated": 1778023145
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7c9e00000000003048f8",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778023582,
      "updated": 1778023584
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7c9f00000000003048fa",
      "text": "\t✂ [GW明け、明日から平常運行できる気がしない]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023584,
      "updated": 1778112003
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad3be0000000000960658",
      "text": "\t[#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk147:Microsoft Officeによるベンダーロックインと実家・スマートEX・シール交換]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778045886,
      "updated": 1778045896
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7c9e00000000003048f9",
      "text": "\t✂ [新幹線の待合室にたくさん退屈した子供がいる]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023582,
      "updated": 1778111901
    },
    {
      "id": "69faea2000000000005d22e1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778051618,
      "updated": 1778051618
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7cca00000000004e6adb",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023626,
      "updated": 1778051270
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7ccc00000000004e6add",
      "text": " 二日ぶりにご飯食べた",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1778023628,
      "updated": 1778023641
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7cd900000000004e6ade",
      "text": "  全粥おいしい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1778023642,
      "updated": 1778023653
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7cca00000000004e6adc",
      "text": "\t\t栄養大事じゃぞ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023626,
      "updated": 1778023652
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa7cde00000000006a6a15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778023647,
      "updated": 1778023647
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa85cc0000000000a14342",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778025932,
      "updated": 1778025934
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa85d10000000000a14343",
      "text": " 起きて3秒カレーの気分",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778025938,
      "updated": 1778025967
    },
    {
      "id": "69fabf5f00000000006b325d",
      "text": " ドーナツの食べたさもある",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778040672,
      "updated": 1778040682
    },
    {
      "id": "69fabf6a00000000006b325e",
      "text": " ドーナツカレー",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778040682,
      "updated": 1778040686
    },
    {
      "id": "69fac1910000000000310910",
      "text": " \t[トンデモ料理]が爆誕している[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778041234,
      "updated": 1778113529
    },
    {
      "id": "69fac1c700000000004bea3e",
      "text": " \t カレーパンのことカレードーナツと言って売ってるのはよく見る[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778041287,
      "updated": 1778041315
    },
    {
      "id": "69facd4a000000000070088b",
      "text": " \t  そうなのか！たしかに[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778044235,
      "updated": 1778044242
    },
    {
      "id": "69facd5b000000000070088c",
      "text": " ✂ [easyジオゲッサー]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778044251,
      "updated": 1778111842
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb1a9d00000000008f924b",
      "text": "\t人間はAIの尻を叩いたり猫の尻を叩いたり忙しい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778064029,
      "updated": 1778064048
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa88140000000000e88197",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a06a49e2ebd480012064bd6",
      "created": 1778026517,
      "updated": 1778026517
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa88160000000000e88199",
      "text": "[yutaro.icon]",
      "userId": "5a06a49e2ebd480012064bd6",
      "created": 1778026519,
      "updated": 1778026520
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa88190000000000e8819a",
      "text": "\t久しぶりに来てみた。社会忙しい",
      "userId": "5a06a49e2ebd480012064bd6",
      "created": 1778026522,
      "updated": 1778026538
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad015000000000053ba77",
      "text": "\t　お久しぶり[基素.icon][yutaro.icon][はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778044950,
      "updated": 1778083344
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa883d0000000000e8819b",
      "text": "\tエンジニア ≒ AIケツ叩きおじさんをがんばってます。",
      "userId": "5a06a49e2ebd480012064bd6",
      "created": 1778026558,
      "updated": 1778026578
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad94e0000000000e8819c",
      "text": "\tソフトウェア開発は、そのソフトウェアを作るために最高のLLM用のハーネスを作る作業に移行してきているような気がする。",
      "userId": "5a06a49e2ebd480012064bd6",
      "created": 1778047310,
      "updated": 1778047339
    },
    {
      "id": "69fad96e0000000000e8819d",
      "text": "\t\tそのゲームやアプリを作る専用の[codex], [claude code]を作っていく作業が最も捗っている",
      "userId": "5a06a49e2ebd480012064bd6",
      "created": 1778047342,
      "updated": 1778047738
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafbd50000000000cc14d9",
      "text": "\t\tつくるソフトウェアとして汎用を目指すほどハーネスも難しくなっていく[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778056150,
      "updated": 1778056167
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa88150000000000e88198",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a06a49e2ebd480012064bd6",
      "created": 1778026517,
      "updated": 1778026517
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa88e300000000005de9ab",
      "text": "[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1778026723,
      "updated": 1778026728
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa88e900000000005de9ad",
      "text": " MacにNixのhome-managerをちょっと入れて、nixを触り始めてる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1778026729,
      "updated": 1778026770
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa891300000000005de9ae",
      "text": "  Nix言語で整える仕組み、OSレベルだけじゃなくて、パッケージマネージャレベル、ユーザレベル、プロジェクトレベル、と、色々な粒度での使い方や仕組みがあるの面白い",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1778026770,
      "updated": 1778026879
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa93080000000000300fe4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1778029321,
      "updated": 1778029321
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa93080000000000300fe6",
      "text": "[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1778029321,
      "updated": 1778029325
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa930d0000000000300fe7",
      "text": " 分厚い本の作りたさ",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1778029326,
      "updated": 1778029394
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa93160000000000300fe8",
      "text": " 昨日と今日は芝居の受付",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1778029334,
      "updated": 1778029427
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa88e300000000005de9ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1778026723,
      "updated": 1778026723
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa96830000000000008d30",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778030211,
      "updated": 1778030211
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa96830000000000008d31",
      "text": " 15?年ぶりの親戚近況を聞いて回ってた",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778030212,
      "updated": 1778030232
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa96a30000000000008d36",
      "text": "  次の世代達は小学生になってた",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778030244,
      "updated": 1778030275
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa96e30000000000008d3d",
      "text": "  昔いとことダークマターで盛り上がってたんだけど、今親戚のひとりが[CERN]で研究してるらしくて面白い",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1778030307,
      "updated": 1778047885
    },
    {
      "id": "69faf4f000000000001294e2",
      "text": "  \t盛り上がりを超えてプロになってる[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778054385,
      "updated": 1778054406
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa96990000000000008d34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1778030234,
      "updated": 1778030234
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa99b40000000000cce48b",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778031029,
      "updated": 1778031030
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa99b60000000000cce48d",
      "text": "　[小泉今日子]の話題にサカナクションの[山口一郎]が言及する形で政治と音楽問題が再燃している",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778031030,
      "updated": 1778031234
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa99d60000000000cce48e",
      "text": "　\tこの話題、一回突っ込んだブログ記事を書きたいと思っている",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778031062,
      "updated": 1778031227
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa99e40000000000cce48f",
      "text": "　\t正直、世間がこの問題について戦時のジャズ禁圧やアイヌ民族に対する文化的虐殺を全く話題にしないことに失望している",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778031076,
      "updated": 1778033032
    },
    {
      "id": "69faa04d0000000000cce491",
      "text": "　[nifty serve]の過去ログ、2012年時点で[ニフティ]社は一部保持していた模様",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778032717,
      "updated": 1778032934
    },
    {
      "id": "69faa0720000000000cce492",
      "text": "　\t有料でもいいから公開してほしい",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778032754,
      "updated": 1778057271
    },
    {
      "id": "69faa0c50000000000cce494",
      "text": "　\t[https://www.cl.ecei.tohoku.ac.jp/publications/2012/infosocio2012_submitted.pdf]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778032837,
      "updated": 1778032839
    },
    {
      "id": "69faa1360000000000cce495",
      "text": "　[5ちゃんねる]はアーカイブ性・反エコチェンのデザインを考慮すると最もまっとうなSNSだと思う",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778032950,
      "updated": 1778057304
    },
    {
      "id": "69faa1470000000000cce496",
      "text": "　\t過去の炎上を当たるには2chしか選択肢ない状況はおかしい",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778032967,
      "updated": 1778032996
    },
    {
      "id": "69fbd7900000000000e2a606",
      "text": "　\t✂ [今国立国会図書館へのアンケ書いてる]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778112400,
      "updated": 1778112431
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb75e50000000000d1814e",
      "text": "　✂ [そういや新建新聞社が報道していた反社実名データベースってどうなったんだろ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778087398,
      "updated": 1778113132
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa99b40000000000cce48c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1778031029,
      "updated": 1778031029
    },
    {
      "id": "69fab3e1000000000007a069",
      "text": "[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1778037730,
      "updated": 1778037731
    },
    {
      "id": "69fbdaab0000000000e2a60a",
      "text": " ✂ [マクドナルドで注文ミスを初めて経験]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778113195,
      "updated": 1778113512
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb11f5000000000007a07e",
      "text": "\t[ザ・スーパーマリオギャラクシー・ムービー]見てきた",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1778061813,
      "updated": 1778061837
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb120c000000000007a07f",
      "text": "\t\t前作が良すぎたために何とも言えない消化不良感",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1778061837,
      "updated": 1778061858
    },
    {
      "id": "69fab3e1000000000007a068",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1778037730,
      "updated": 1778037730
    },
    {
      "id": "69faeeb400000000008065a3",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778052788,
      "updated": 1778052788
    },
    {
      "id": "69faeeb400000000008065a4",
      "text": "\t>エンジニア ≒ AIケツ叩きおじさん",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778052789,
      "updated": 1778052794
    },
    {
      "id": "69faeeba00000000008065a5",
      "text": "\t\t叩くだなんて暴力的だ！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778052794,
      "updated": 1778052806
    },
    {
      "id": "69faeec600000000008065a6",
      "text": "\t\tケツなんて言葉下品！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778052806,
      "updated": 1778052815
    },
    {
      "id": "69faeecf00000000008065a7",
      "text": "\t\t→AIおしりさわりおじさん(余計悪い)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778052815,
      "updated": 1778052832
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb4b2a00000000004aef0c",
      "text": "\t\t　最悪で笑う[基素.icon][yutaro.icon]",
      "userId": "5a06a49e2ebd480012064bd6",
      "created": 1778076459,
      "updated": 1778083038
    },
    {
      "id": "69faeee000000000008065a8",
      "text": "\t首カチカチ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778052832,
      "updated": 1778053041
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb1b7100000000008065aa",
      "text": "\t[Magic Bar ENCORE https://magicbar-encore.jp/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778064243,
      "updated": 1778064243
    },
    {
      "id": "69faefa400000000008065a9",
      "text": "\t\tMagic Bar ENCORE、真相にたどり着きました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778053028,
      "updated": 1778065693
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb21200000000000103172",
      "text": "\t\t24分",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778065696,
      "updated": 1778065698
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb21230000000000103173",
      "text": "\t\tきっかけ投稿: https://x.com/ryuka_magic/status/2047660545852268987",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778065700,
      "updated": 1778066307
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb23830000000000103174",
      "text": "\t[愛宝学園かがみの特殊少年更生施設 https://kagamino-jrep.net/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778066309,
      "updated": 1778066456
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb24180000000000103175",
      "text": "　　ボリューム多い！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778066457,
      "updated": 1778075641
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb47f90000000000d43a15",
      "text": "\t\t飽きたのでやめた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778075641,
      "updated": 1778083401
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb72870000000000e81090",
      "text": "\t\tなんか[~ 漫画読む]やつだ[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778086536,
      "updated": 1778120735
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb47f90000000000d43a16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1778075641,
      "updated": 1778075641
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafc850000000000c6fd90",
      "text": "[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778056326,
      "updated": 1778056327
    },
    {
      "id": "69fafc850000000000c6fd91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778056326,
      "updated": 1778056326
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb09e50000000000fa8a85",
      "text": "[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778059750,
      "updated": 1778059750
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb09e50000000000fa8a86",
      "text": " プログラミング経験の差/LLM活用度の差が大きい人と共同でアプリ開発するの大変",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778059750,
      "updated": 1778059829
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0a140000000000fa8a89",
      "text": " 　99%AI製のアプリができるとか、セキュリティが～とかいろいろ言われてるところではない",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778059797,
      "updated": 1778059993
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0a3a0000000000fa8a8a",
      "text": " 　講習会とかハッカソンとか、ただ作ればいいのではなくて「実際に\"一緒に\"作ってみよう」の文脈",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778059835,
      "updated": 1778059928
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0adc0000000000fa8a92",
      "text": " 　 アイデアとか何が必要かな～からスタックとか考えるのは一緒にできる",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778059997,
      "updated": 1778060020
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0af60000000000fa8a93",
      "text": "  　 さて、実際に作ってみようとなったときに私がAIに指示するのだとみんなが手持無沙汰になる",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778060023,
      "updated": 1778060068
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0b230000000000fa8a94",
      "text": "  　 　作った感もないだろう",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778060068,
      "updated": 1778060070
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb134c0000000000fa8a98",
      "text": "  　 　進まないのを覚悟で、コード部分は任せつつ基盤とか必要なアセットを作る係になろうかしら",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778062156,
      "updated": 1778062191
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb136f0000000000fa8a99",
      "text": "  　 　　初心者でもAIを使って開発できるという前提に立っているが...",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778062192,
      "updated": 1778062206
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0b300000000000fa8a95",
      "text": "  　逆に100%AI(エージェント)コーディング禁止、バグ取りとか(弱い)補完、アイデアとかコマンドの使い方をAIに質問する",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778060081,
      "updated": 1778060136
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0b710000000000fa8a97",
      "text": "  　　2023~2024年的AIコーディング",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778060145,
      "updated": 1778060164
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0b680000000000fa8a96",
      "text": "  　　これはめっちゃいい使い方だったと思う",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778060137,
      "updated": 1778060143
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb9bc20000000000e44756",
      "text": "　書きながら考えてる[/discordwiki/pencil.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778097091,
      "updated": 1778097131
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5ef800000000000c08c3",
      "text": "　\tｴﾗｲｯ[imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778081529,
      "updated": 1778081535
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb0a7c0000000000fa8a8b",
      "text": " AIｹﾂ叩き兄さんをやらせていただいてます",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778059901,
      "updated": 1778059916
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb30f600000000008e5b70",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1778069751,
      "updated": 1778069751
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb30f600000000008e5b71",
      "text": "[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1778069751,
      "updated": 1778069752
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb30f800000000008e5b72",
      "text": " SpotifyのAPIからAudio Featuresを取得したいんだけど、最近かなり制約があるようで取得できない。",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1778069752,
      "updated": 1778069786
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb09e60000000000fa8a87",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1778059750,
      "updated": 1778059750
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb4b3400000000004aef0d",
      "text": "[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1778076469,
      "updated": 1778076470
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb4b5700000000004aef10",
      "text": "　はしかが流行りつつあるらしい",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1778076504,
      "updated": 1778076509
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb4b3600000000004aef0f",
      "text": "　　https://idsc.tmiph.metro.tokyo.lg.jp/diseases/measles/measles/",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1778076470,
      "updated": 1778076510
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5ede00000000000c08c2",
      "text": "　　\tひえー[imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778081503,
      "updated": 1778081504
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb4b5e00000000004aef11",
      "text": "　ワクチン接種の棚卸しをして、二種混合を1回しか受けていなかったのを知ったので2回目をうけた",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1778076510,
      "updated": 1778076558
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb4b8f00000000004aef12",
      "text": "　HPVの自費ってお高いんだな〜",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1778076560,
      "updated": 1778076593
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb4b8f00000000004aef13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1778076560,
      "updated": 1778076560
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5aa700000000000c08b9",
      "text": "[imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778080424,
      "updated": 1778080425
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5aa900000000000c08bb",
      "text": "\tクロッキーに停滞感を感じてきたので欲求に従いサボり",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778080425,
      "updated": 1778080512
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5ac700000000000c08bc",
      "text": " \tとはいえこの手のトレーニングは無心で続けるべきものなのではないかという疑いもある",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778080455,
      "updated": 1778080879
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5ae900000000000c08bd",
      "text": "  でもAnkiの分散学習みたいに何もしない期間を設けるのもいいのかもしれない（都合の良い解釈）",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778080490,
      "updated": 1778080879
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb6633000000000076dcf1",
      "text": "   w[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1778083379,
      "updated": 1778083382
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5c0000000000000c08be",
      "text": " 毎日ちょっとでも描けない構図を鍛えようという意識でやった",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778080769,
      "updated": 1778081006
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5cee00000000000c08c0",
      "text": " \t習慣化すれば立ち上がりはスムーズになるかなと思ったがそんなことはなく、毎日「面倒臭いな…」という心理は働いていた",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778081006,
      "updated": 1778081879
    },
    {
      "id": "69fc15430000000000cbe5e4",
      "text": " \t 毎日別のかけないものを描いていたら常に負荷がかかりそう[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1778128196,
      "updated": 1778128213
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb5c5e00000000000c08bf",
      "text": " \t結構続いてきたからもったいないなーという心理もあった、ソシャゲみたいなものかもしれない",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778080862,
      "updated": 1778081414
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb697f00000000003d7fb8",
      "text": " サボるつもりだったがなんかソワソワしてきたので普通にやった",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778084224,
      "updated": 1778084273
    },
    {
      "id": "69fc01ea0000000000ee24ae",
      "text": "  えらすぎ[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778123243,
      "updated": 1778123246
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb69b000000000003d7fb9",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/9b9f21b5ab48bc435ca8fff8785976cb]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1778084273,
      "updated": 1778084278
    },
    {
      "id": "69fbc3e40000000000601c0f",
      "text": " よい[takker.icon][Hiro Aki.icon][nishio.icon][caki.icon][基素.icon][bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778107364,
      "updated": 1778136275
    },
    {
      "id": "69fc30f100000000009a4994",
      "text": " \tええやろ！！[imo.icon]",
